description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Salamander Yoga! | 5-minute Yoga Break | Scratch Garden' from the channel Scratch Garden.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Take a fun five-minute yoga break with Salamander!

Relax your mind and body while you practice breathing and stretching as we demonstrate various yoga poses, including mountain pose, star pose, boat pose, and more! This fun brain break video is perfect for introducing mindfulness and even practicing yoga for beginners.
